Ken Vander Weele, Secretary
Ken Vander Weele is one of the Advisory Board members of Creation Investments Social Ventures Fund I, II and III. He is the Secretary of the Board and is a member of the Fund’s Valuation Committee. Select Management Team for a further biography.
.
.
