Creation Investments Social Ventures Fund IIi  Form D
The Illinois-based Creation Investments Social Ventures Fund IIi, L.P.  released  D Form  for $68.32 million offering. This is a new filing.  The Limited Partnership raised $68.32 million. The offering is still open. The total  private offering amount amount was $68.32 million.  The offering form was filed on 2015-07-14. Creation Investments Social Ventures Fund IIi, L.P.’s clarification was: unspecified. 
 Creation Investments Social Ventures Fund IIi  is based in Illinois. The  firm’s business is Pooled Investment Fund. The  SEC form was  submitted by Patrick T Fisher Managing Partner of the general partner of the Issuer.  The company was incorporated in 2015. The filler’s address is: 30 South Wacker Drive, Suite 1600, Chicago, Il, Illinois, 60606.  Patrick T. Fisher is the related person in the form and it has address: 30 South Wacker, Suite 1600, Chicago, Il, Illinois, 60606. Link to Creation Investments Social Ventures Fund IIi  Filing: 000164726315000001.
Analysis of Creation Investments Social Ventures Fund IIi  Offering
On average,  startups in the Pooled Investment Fund sector, sell 37.80%  pooled investment interest. Creation Investments Social Ventures Fund IIi  sold 100.00% of the offering. The average  investment offering size is $24.76 million for companies in the Pooled Investment Fund industry sector. The minimum investment for Creation Investments Social Ventures Fund IIi ‘s  private offering  is $30000.

